<span id="freeTextContainer1173790199736233815">I really enjoyed this one... I&apos;ve forgotten how much I enjoy James&apos; writing. I had never read the Cordelia Gray series and when I finished this one I was so disappointed to learn that there are no more! <br/>This was an island mystery- not quite up to the standard of &apos;And There Were None&apos;, but that&apos;s pretty much the pinnacle of British island-based mystery novels so it&apos;s a hard mark to hit. </span>
